OL,3,CSuicide attempts rising at asylum
OL,4,Cseeker site RAF Wethersfield
OL,6,FCharities have warned of a "mental
OL,7,Fhealth crisis" among asylum seekers
OL,8,Fhoused at RAF Wethersfield, with
OL,9,Fincidents of suicide attempts and self-
OL,10,Fharm at the site rising.
OL,12,FThere were between five and 10 suicide
OL,13,Fattempts and 10 incidents of self-harm
OL,14,Fin January 2024 alone at the site in
OL,15,FEssex - the highest since the site
OL,16,Fopened in July 2023 - according to
OL,17,Fdata exclusively given to ITV News by
OL,18,Fthe Helen Bamber Foundation and
OL,19,FDoctors of the World.
