OL,6,FBut Home Secretary James Cleverly said
OL,7,Fpeople weren't telling the truth about.
OL,9,FResponding to ITV News' findings, Mr
OL,10,FCleverly said: "The simple truth is,
OL,11,Foften when people come to this country
OL,12,Fillegally they do lie to further their
OL,13,Fown causes."
OL,15,FWethersfield is one of a number of
OL,16,Fmass accommodation sites being used
OL,17,Falongside hotels to house asylum
OL,18,Fseekers. They're particularly
OL,19,Fcontroversial because of their remote
OL,20,Flocations, and the fact they're
OL,21,Fremoved from local communities.
