OL,6,FRAF Wethersfield and the Bibby
OL,7,FStockholm barge in Dorset have been
OL,8,Foperating since last summer. In
OL,9,FDecember last year, Another former RAF
OL,10,Fbase in Scampton is yet to open, along
OL,11,Fwith former student accommodation in
OL,12,FHuddersfield.
OL,14,FRAF Wethersfield only accommodates
OL,15,Fmen, most of whom have come to the UK
OL,16,Fon small boats. The 580 men currently
OL,17,Fat the site are stuck in limbo, as the
OL,18,Fgovernment's new Illegal Migration Act
OL,19,Fmeans the Home Office won't consider
OL,20,Fthe claims of those who arrive in the
OL,21,FUK via small boats.
