OL,6,FITV News spoke to one asylum seeker
OL,7,Fwho spent over six months at
OL,8,FWethersfield before being removed
OL,9,Fbecause of his deteriorating mental
OL,10,Fhealth.
OL,12,FThe 25-year-old man, who asked to
OL,13,Fremain anonymous and we are calling
OL,14,FAli, came over to the UK in a small
OL,15,Fboat in September 2023 after fleeing
OL,16,Fthe Taliban in Afghanistan. He left
OL,17,Fafter the Taliban shot him and killed
OL,18,Fhis brother.
