OL,6,FAli described the moment he arrived at
OL,7,FWethersfield: "I was thinking we're in
OL,8,Fprison, we're coming to the prison.
OL,9,FWhat did we do wrong?".
OL,11,FHe told ITV News about how his mental
OL,12,Fhealth had worsened while he was at
OL,13,Fthe site. After never having any
OL,14,Fprevious mental health issues, he was
OL,15,Fdiagnosed with depression at
OL,16,FWethersfield, and even tried to take
OL,17,Fhis own life.
OL,19,FAli said he ended up in hospital after
OL,20,Fhe jumped from a window.
