OL,6,FHe said he witnessed abuse by security
OL,7,Fguards at the site, with staff
OL,8,Ffrequently telling him and others to
OL,9,F"F*** off" and "go back to your
OL,10,Fcountry".
OL,12,FITV News has also seen video evidence
OL,13,Fof poor conditions inside the site -
OL,14,Fsecurity guards swearing at residents,
OL,15,Ffights breaking out between rival
OL,16,Fgroups in the camp, people desperately
OL,17,Ftrying to throw themselves off
OL,18,Fbuildings, and the sound of gunshots
OL,19,Fheard at a clay pigeon shooting range
OL,20,Fnext to the site.
