OL,6,FThe, with a recent report from the
OL,7,Fspending watchdog showing the
OL,8,Faccommodation is costing 10 times more
OL,9,Fthan originally planned.
OL,11,FThe National Audit Office (NAO) said
OL,12,Fthe Home Office originally estimated
OL,13,Fset-up costs at RAF Wethersfield would
OL,14,Fbe #5 million,.
OL,16,FThe report also said there had been
OL,17,F283 incidents relating to "self-harm
OL,18,Fand suicide" at large sites like
OL,19,FWethersfield by the end of January
OL,20,F2024.
