OL,6,FThree days a week a medical van
OL,7,Foperated by charity Doctors of the
OL,8,FWorld parks up outside Wethersfield to
OL,9,Ftreat residents. While there are
OL,10,Fmedical services inside, charities say
OL,11,Fthey don't provide adequate care for
OL,12,Fthe vulnerable asylum seekers living
OL,13,Fat the site.
OL,15,FA survey of 122 patients revealed 70%
OL,16,Fwere presenting with severe
OL,17,Fpsychological distress and 41% were
OL,18,Fexperiencing suicidal thoughts.
