OL,6,FClinical Director Becks Kerr said "if
OL,7,Fyou put people in a place like this,
OL,8,Fyou're asking for a mental health
OL,9,Fcrisis".
OL,11,F"Anyone deserves to be treated with
OL,12,Fdignity and humanity, in particular
OL,13,Fpeople coming to this country with
OL,14,Fexperience of violence and trauma,"
OL,15,Fshe said.
OL,17,FThe use of the site is even being
OL,18,Fchallenged in the courts.
