OL,6,FLaw firm Duncan Lewis is bringing a
OL,7,Fcase against the Home Office which
OL,8,Fsays they have failed to properly
OL,9,Fassess whether vulnerable people
OL,10,Fshould be living at Wethersfield.
OL,12,FITV News spoke exclusively to
OL,13,Fbarrister Shalini Patel who says the
OL,14,Fsite is like a "detention centre",
OL,15,Fequating to "false imprisonment".
OL,17,FMs Patel said she feels "extremely
OL,18,Fworried" about the conditions inside
OL,19,FWethersfield.
