OL,9,FOffice's policy very clearly states
OL,10,Fvictims of torture, victims of
OL,11,Ftrafficking, anyone with mental health
OL,12,For physical disabilities should not be
OL,13,Faccommodated at the site, yet we have
OL,14,Fbeen instructed by tens of
